# TLSNotary 2PC under min_mix_hops=3 - Detailed Metrics + Diagram
# Captured from the instrumented run of crates/examples/basic/basic.rs (2026-06-07)
# The test: simulation client (verifier role) + expert (prover role) performing
# a full 2PC TLSNotary session where the prover dials a target (fixture standing in for Anthropic).
# The prover<->verifier MPC channel had 8 artificial 375ms one-way sleeps injected at phase
# boundaries to simulate messages traveling over a 3-hop mixnet path (750ms RTT aggregate,
# ~125ms effective per hop).

